Before merging LLM-based features:

- [ ] Tests use OpenRouter with proper configuration
- [ ] Tests focus on business logic, not Zod validation
- [ ] Tests use realistic data (not mocks)
- [ ] Tests verify determinism (temperature 0)
- [ ] Tests check content quality (not generic)
- [ ] Tests verify data usage (actual tokens/amounts)
- [ ] Integration tests with real services
- [ ] Performance tests for acceptable response times
- [ ] Tests are properly organized and documented
